    "More details (e.g., GPT instructions) are described in Appendix A.",
    "Comparison with State-of-the-art ApproachesTable 2 summarizes quantitative results for two popular diffusion models [1,5].",
    "With similar inference cost, ISAC clearly outperforms existing approaches on every metric of HRS-Bench, T2I-CompBench, and the multi-class setting of IntraCompBench.",
    "The largest improvements appear in the intra-category regime: on SD1.5 [1], the average multi-class accuracy on IntraCompBench increases from 20% for the strongest baseline [2] to 36% with ISAC, and the HRS-Bench spatial score is roughly doubled (0.127 to 0.263).",
    "On the stronger SD3.5-M backbone, ISAC still provides a clear margin with especially large gains in the more crowded #4 and #5 cases."
